    "We can hence close this non-causal path by conditioning on Rigour.",
    "In addition, Rigour acts as a confounder on the non-causal path Open data ← Rigour → Reproducibility.",
    "To identify the causal effect, we hence also need to close this noncausal path by conditioning on Rigour.",
    "In short, we close both non-causal paths by conditioning on Rigour.",
    "Panel A in Figure 7 shows the DAG for this question."
